tweet: The Committee on Agriculture,Animal Industry and Fisheries is scrutinizing the Fisheries and Aquaculture Bill,2021. Members of the public are invited to submit their views on the bill in writing to the Office of the Clerk to Parliament or email at clerk@parliament.go.ug
name: Parliament of Uganda
